{"tid":1546324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【警察請入】對中共而言，警隊係赤化香港既最大憂慮","createTime":"2019-09-06T08:46:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T05:27:22.000Z","uid":13138,"like":70,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"6638bb5fea2ba874f44abadd8c695a962ab920ba","tid":1546324,"uid":13138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:46:15.000Z","msg":"發展大灣區 想令香港邊界模糊化 赤化香港 做既第一樣一定會係幫警隊換血 因為暫時黎講 你地仲係唯一自由係香港執法既武裝部隊<br />\n<br />\n雖然話唔同政見 但你地係土生土長香港人 對香港有歸屬感 愛唔愛國自己心知肚明 加上受過訓練 有武裝 你估大陸驚你地定我地多啲？自己諗下<br />\n<br />\n香港警民關係90年後一直都好 至少冇人會阻住你地做野 好配合你地 治安係成為世界美譽 <br />\n<br />\n大陸知道直接出政策幫警隊換血係一定冇可能 仲會團結埋香港人 even係雨傘/魚蛋之後警民都算融洽 就拎上年深水埗mtr開槍黎講 你地最憎既連登仔係讚緊警察開槍開得好 無疑係對你地有信任先會咁講<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">深水埗港鐵站發生開槍事件　警方封鎖現場調查<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/892380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/892380</a></span><br />\n<br />\n當真係比你地捉曬打死曬啲示威者 冇人再咁出黎 咁又點 大陸下一個開刀就係你地 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">因為冇香港人會贏</span></span><br />\n大陸論壇已經吹曬風叫警察送仔女返大陸讀書 何妖叫警察返大陸退休 目標係揸住你地春袋 依家已經為大灣區執法部門一體化鋪緊路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋留唔留意到你身邊講普通話既*同事*特別重手 因為到時都係你地*香港警察*幫佢地食死貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff6f55d714c34ce265a232a544fcdabbf01428f2","tid":1546324,"uid":13138,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:46:26.000Z","msg":"香港人對你地失望既後果 就係到你地送中/比人重組唔會再有人幫你地 到時大陸人會係你地阿頭 你香港人既身份永遠會比中共標籤 成為最底層 本身的薪酬福利就同上面睇齊 什至更差<br />\n<br />\n雨傘魚蛋 商家佬覺得普選制度自由社會唔關佢事 佢地覺得示威者搞搞震 阻住佢地搵錢<br />\n到逃犯條例 商家佬好多都驚到要走資 到警察覺得示威者破壞安寧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想講總有一日到你地後悔  依家已經開始續步清算你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇下下面2個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">［超突發］中國公安將全面取代香港警察<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545420\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545420</a><br />\nMon post警員聽住：你哋上司想割蓆自保啦，快啲backup所有對話、錄音<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545969\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545969</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所有香港人只有一齊贏同一齊輸依條路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"062956837019bbe7e5519d90aa0a250d3063fd15","tid":1546324,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:47:32.000Z","msg":"7/9機場更新 求求大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545323</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fg5HKFh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFg5HKFh.jpg&h=b79850f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=42d6dd9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"29dd85f2dbffa2baab9d93085e31ccb51b63fcab","tid":1546324,"uid":13138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:47:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"214a2585178a4d4330dfb9fbaecaaf0adbead1d5","tid":1546324,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:47:40.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99480bf5b114ca19143a18e601bacd530238b248","tid":1546324,"uid":282587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cite