\" />"},{"pid":"4561683c6ef564dcfd1a016013be321b1bf0cc71","tid":1546324,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T09:11:53.000Z","msg":"依家果班個個月ot幾皮就夠 唔洗考慮後果 講多無謂"},{"pid":"1728b8ccc5ed7aa96cca624f13709a6d7a531fa4","tid":1546324,"uid":13138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T09:13:11.000Z","msg":"唔該幫我推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"430b14b9183c4a5ccf10aa929a186bbebef0a1c3","tid":1546324,"uid":13138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef568d350fca9536c380d5d7d0bc67d2e5e44377","tid":1546324,"uid":290678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:59:06.000Z","msg":"以畜生既智慧 應該睇完都唔明你講乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係呀 講緊你呀 Mon Po狗 轉下個閪腦喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T09:39:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36bba4efadbaa0c15dabc6fa77933506358d6be2","tid":1546324,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T09:40:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n👉🏻<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>中英聯合聲明的謬誤</ins></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n若果一件物件是從來未曾擁有過，拿到手上是談不上「恢復」及「收回」的。同樣道理，1997年前中華人民共和國從來未曾對香港行使過主權，如何談得上「恢復行使主權」？中華人民共和國的漢族（即「中國人民」）從來也沒有擁有過香港，試問又如何「收回」香港？<br />\n<br />\n因此，中華人民共和國取得香港的土地應該形容為「兼併」或「呑併」。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n👉🏻<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>不平等條約無效論是謊言</ins></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如兩國以和平條約（Peace Treaty）終止戰爭，而某些領土由一國割讓予另一國，則在國際法中亦被視為透過割讓（Cession）而取得主權。過去的國際法觀點認為，以戰爭解決國與國之間的爭議屬國家的權利，而「和平條約」的作用是令交戰雙方以某些條款（包括部份領土的轉讓）為代價以終止戰爭。因此，按照「時空性原則」，1842年及1860年割讓香港島及九龍半島均符合當時的國際法。<br />\n<br />\n國際法中，領土的轉讓只有是否合法，而沒有平等不平等。<br />\n<br />\n在中華人民共和國成為國家之前，英國已經從清帝國手中符合國際法地取得香港的主權。另一方面，中華人民共和國亦從來沒有繼承過清帝國的仼何權益。因此，《中英聯合聲明》中所謂「對香港恢復行使主權」的「恢復」根本無從談起，並且只是一個猜想。</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cbwr6sW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCbwr6sW.png&h=7ee87500&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tPAHEN9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtPAHEN9.png&h=e166e8fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n知情不報者 你地都係半個兇手！<br />\n你唯一可以做就係站出黎 講個真相比全香港市民聽！ ！ 還死者一個清白！</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">肛犬：<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n別再喱係電視後面，敢就走出黎攞出CCTV之類証據黎証明831冇人死冇人重傷囉仆街共狗！！！</span></span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/05/104231_3a6ab00f3ec1c5387f321c23ffcf1893.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F05%2F104231_3a6ab00f3ec1c5387f321c23ffcf1893.jpg&h=7d68f7dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">必問：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有幾倍OT收，係咪仲要&quot;好合理要屌埋女示者&quot;咁辛苦？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>民主訴求，缺一不可；<br />\n<br />\n以眼還眼，鷹犬全鎖；<br />\n<br />\n有錯企定，即決勿拖！<br />\n<br />\n民主斬件，仲當我傻！<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，未贏收科？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</strong></span></span></span></span><br />\n<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">除非你係個班那埋護照旁身嘅扮民霸權，永續利益獨賣囉！！！</span></span></span></span></strong></strong>"},{"pid":"644ce0c7ecc83d0c9c5cd2c4d92ce8dab83ab240","tid":1546324,"uid":20134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T09:43:50.000Z","msg":"講黑警對佢地班仆街唔會有影響<br />\n可以試下講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>你班共產黨既走狗</strong></span>"},{"pid":"d86340ff392c05a03ced0795cdbf25d418bca7c7","tid":1546324,"uid":126947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T09:47:39.000Z","msg":"牠們無咁高智商去消化你篇文"},{"pid":"f011728b09be4c261e4473e6055f0a32b32a150e","tid":1546324,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8161aff2402f2180dda0cc8a1adaa0ae2c9465d7","tid":1546324,"uid":13138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T09:10:50.000Z","msg":"冇香港人會贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T09:48:16.000Z","msg":"屌，嘥氣喇，做乜都太遲"},{"pid":"c1b34c9fcaac0158a83e863647d4afc3e4526912","tid":1546324,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T09:51:24.000Z","msg":"班蠢閪點會知呀 仲當緊自己係正義超人"},{"pid":"fc199e71d2df88578f894b1243afd1f045791001","tid":1546324,"uid":45727,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T09:53:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"co